text: Long gone, mate. Long gone.
You were all a pleasure to watch. So thank you xx

A big thank you to everyone who has contributed to #joinin today. It is nothing without you. Sending lots of love to those of you who found today hard. I hope the smashers of #joinin helped in some small way. I am lighting a candle for all of those you’ve lost.pic.twitter.com/KFv9TAA2h9

A top up of love to all those using the #joinin hashtag. You are filling my heart and each others’ with joy. Remember to always include the hashtag #joinin and don’t wait for someone to chat to you. Just dive in and get chatting. X

Thank you to everyone who is chatting on #joinin. If you are feeling rubbish and would like some company, make yourself known. And always use the hashtag #joinin so that everyone can see you. Love to all.
We’ve opened the biscuits. #joinin Dive in, everyone. pic.twitter.com/M90OeU011j

You okay? Xx

Ah you’re so welcome. It’s all the smashers on here that make #joinin what it is. Sorry you have tough family members to deal with but I think that’s the case for a lot of people. It’s just a day at least! I’m good thanks. Everyone else is asleep here, even the animals!
How are you doing today Catriona? #joinin
Oh God. That’s bloody terrible. So sorry. Have you got anyone with you? #joinin

Hi Allie, sorry you’re feeling teary. I think that’s pretty normal at this time of you. It’s not christmas unless we’ve all had a little cry. Have you got any plans for today? Go out for a walk? Watch some telly? Eat something nice? #joinin

I can see how that is tough. Is there a member of your family who is good to you? Could you stick to them? And yay for chocolate for breakfast. I was just wondering if that was allowed and you have given me permission! Xx #joinin

Hiya Suzy, that does all sound very tough indeed. You’re a good one for not leaving your dad. Poor man. And poor you. Time will ease your pain but I know that doesn’t help you right now. Got anything nice in for you and dad to eat? Got any telly plans? #joinin
Hello! What time is it in Arizona? #joinin
Sorry to hear that, Alexander. Sending lots of love and hugs. Got any plans for telly later? #joinin

Great tip! #joinin

Thanks Grace. You’re a star. #joinin
Ah much love to you and your little boy. Thank him for the note please? Got any telly plans today? #joinin
Agreed, Alison. It enriches the soul. #joinin Beautiful pics.
We’re all here, Sophie. Got anything nice in to eat? #joinin
Also, that cake looks cracking. #joinin

Hi Marianne, so sorry you’re having such a rough time of it. I got divorced after 8 years and I can honestly say it’s one of the best things that happened to me. Easy to say that now as it’s 14 years ago but it will get easier. So sorry for your loss too. Sending love. #joinin

If anyone needs a laugh today, have a look at the #DuvetKnowItsChrismas hashtag set up by the brilliant @rhodri where folk share their Christmas sleeping arrangements in relatives houses. It’s worth a look and a giggle.
Ah that’s very kind of you to say. I love watching comedy when I feel crap. It really helps. Would I Lie to You is a good one too. #joinin
Thanks!
@LPC1231 How are you this morning, Leigh? What time are you off to your friend’s house? #joinin x
I was joining in at 2:30am when you were in the land of nod, you cheeky bugger. And you better not have had any of my strawberry creams! #joinin
Sending lots of love, Margaret. Sorry you’ve had a tough time but glad you’re getting through it. #joinin
So sorry for your loss, Dave. Stick with us on here today. Have you got any telly plans later? And tea is coming up. #joinin
Hiya Emma, how are you doing? Got any telly plans later? #joinin
So sorry for your loss, Noelle. I’m glad you have your Mom. Sending hugs to you both. #joinin
Hiya Luna, have you got any telly plans later? #joinin

Morning all and a Merry Christmas to each and every one of you. If you want some company - feeling lonely or low - then we are here. Always use the hashtag #joinin, that way people can see you. Let yourself be known to us. I’ve got the kettle on. Who wants a cuppa?pic.twitter.com/4gGlI0Di6C
Haha. 1982, you’re just a bairn! Sleep well, Leigh. Speak in the morning. X #joinin
Please do. Also, what’s your first name? Feels silly calling you LPC1231. And thank you @paulross for bringing you to us! #joinin
Accepted! I’ll take all I can get.

For those doing #joinin, click the hashtag and get chatting to people there. There are people who are needing some company there right now. You can make contact, listen, make them smile. Thank you from the bottom of my heart.
I’m so sorry for your loss, Lany. Sending lots of love and hugs to you. #joinin
I will hold you to that. I’m so looking forward to that photo. And let’s see re IT. Let’s chat in the morning again. Get some sleep. And I’m glad you’ve made some pals tonight. #joinin
What is it you normally do for a living? Let’s see if anyone out there tomorrow can help you. #joinin
I’m so sorry you’re having such a tough time. Stick to Twitter tomorrow. We’ll all be here if you need us. Sending lots of love and hugs to you. Xxx

Also, you can totally cry. If you don’t feel like you can cry to your pal and his family (I’m sure you could) then go to the loo and have a few tears. I’ve cried on so many trains, love. It really helps to let it out. Talk to your friend if you can. Or us, talk to us #joinin

When I’m low, a friend told me this which I find helps. “Just because this is how you feel right now, doesn’t mean it’s how you’ll always feel.” That helps me. Knowing that everything is always changing. Will you be seeing your daughter soon? I’m sure she’s looking forward to it.

Hi, I’m sorry you’re having such a tough time. I know you think everyone is happy at this time of year but that’s what adverts make us think. Most people are just getting through it. You’re not fucked up. You’re just having a shitty time, flower. 1/2

Right, lovely Twitter people. I’m off to bed and will see you tomorrow for #joinin should you fancy it. If you’re in a part of the world where it’s already morning, feel free to get started without me. Here’s how it works.pic.twitter.com/frkeZ7tyhR
